"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QLsW7blcB13Y4i1s2FYw8.png?height=325&width=955)\\n\\n Mantle Finance是 Flow 主网上可以将 NFT 借贷和 DeFi 应用结合起来，这给所有基于 Flow 的 NFT 收集者带来方便。\\n\\n在 Flow 上整合“流动性”，将会在很多方面对生态有很大的帮助。对于 Flow 上的海量 NFT 收集者来说，它的流动性和资金效率可以同时得到提升。Mantle Finance 的存在是为了增强和整合 NFT 和加密资产的流动性。\\n\\n目前官方测试空投活动进行中\\n\\n1）测试[填表](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScN4XnkZwa7A5I_aX6SaIBuW2Q7lVCKPlMtF_YroWjqE_8i6w/viewform)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/F_SmLWBg6lWVQhIcajAMd.png?height=487&width=634)\\n\\n2）社区活动[填表](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScN4XnkZwa7A5I_aX6SaIBuW2Q7lVCKPlMtF_YroWjqE_8i6w/viewform)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/M1gUKLWuFkJQ0CD-9c7rQ.png?height=190&width=596)\\n\\n下面开始我们的测试教程：\\n\\n1）进入[测试页面](https://testnet.flow.mantlefi.com/nft-lending/beta-test-airdrop)，建立钱包。先连接右上钱包\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4aiM9KU32McQqicuFsESf.png?height=223&width=262)\\n\\n2）选择Blocto钱包。填写邮箱，输入验证码即可。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BVMr5coWFlkT9srAk4RN5.png?height=470&width=386)\\n\\n3）在页面最下面找到申请测试币，钱包授权即可\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/a07-2Y18TgoYwUgysuTRh.png?height=332&width=645)\\n\\n![成功](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/G4irsI_Jhx6pbxfh45l8V.png?height=324&width=406)\\n\\n4）**NFT贷款**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lmWSWLNuf5alXrSrqP0xp.png?height=930&width=1364)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_sLF25fgj2VzEo-onoYb5.png?height=622&width=891)\\n\\n![钱包授权即可](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FfOTx5IvmQA4Bd49eODrC.png?height=543&width=424)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WW0HmBlp-up4KBP-tRn3w.png?height=315&width=417)\\n\\n![贷款中的跟抵押中的在页面上部可以看到](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fPIo8gA0A3ef0sv9xk2vP.png?height=646&width=1131)\\n\\n5）借贷。找到Collateral\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-SHPgS9Nj5iqvQZ52AqHY.png?height=158&width=610)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642074244,\"title\":\"Mantle Finance测试空投教程\"},\"digest\":\"soO7-tC8oNMwdeO9mGjh-2-4JJ70fjl0JK1qJugFLww\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x232F9B36Fb579a71034dc21A467c921eec01FAA9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"q3G1pFxUQxAjc7n1BpuOdIyi5OPkngh__hNUPF4bwNk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xg2td5GN7KgLaTDM9H9sPU6iTzvVoBzNzfOzdVPgJRo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ytBEkoB8xQ6yRpbCtLVkpBBacix2d1mvuPiA_VDYz9n5BV-GZqszVxWS_4pLlt8-f98dSozLtKQDMbUxlFcc5Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xbe0b8139cc8d6535086008b730f3472efdf604fcbd3cf21b05b4391f266dcc214b40849e4e0d31c7c312ab5838857f5039bbc41adbe198262e44df581a0a2d6b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"q3G1pFxUQxAjc7n1BpuOdIyi5OPkngh__hNUPF4bwNk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xg2td5GN7KgLaTDM9H9sPU6iTzvVoBzNzfOzdVPgJRo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"soO7-tC8oNMwdeO9mGjh-2-4JJ70fjl0JK1qJugFLww\"}"